18	// TestServerBoundedEgress verifies FEAT-022 §10 / §11 — every in-scope MCP
19	// and REST surface that inlines library-doc, execution-bundle, diff,
20	// session, or persona content runs the body through evidence.ClampOutput
21	// and exposes truncated/original_bytes metadata.
22	//
23	// Each subtest issues a request (or direct call for non-handler entry
